<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Translation modes</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Simply Readable offers several ways to translate content:
</p>

<div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-!-margin-top-4">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
    <div class="ndx-feature-card">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Create Translation Job</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
        Upload files (.txt, .docx, .html, .xlsx, .pptx) and translate into one or more languages.
        Jobs are tracked in history.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
    <div class="ndx-feature-card">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Quick Text</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
        Instant text translation. Type or paste text and get immediate results.
        Ideal for quick translations of short communications.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
    <div class="ndx-feature-card">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Quick Translate</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
        Fast file translation that downloads results directly without creating a
        persistent job record. Best for one-off document translations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Language auto-detection</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  The tool uses <strong>Amazon Comprehend</strong> to automatically detect the source language
  of your text. You don't need to specify what language the original document is in -
  the tool figures it out. This is powered by the same AI that processes millions of
  documents across AWS.
</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Real-world use cases</h3>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-list--spaced">
  <li><strong>Council tax notices</strong> - translate annually for all community languages in your area</li>
  <li><strong>Public health communications</strong> - rapid translation during health emergencies</li>
  <li><strong>Planning notifications</strong> - ensure affected residents can understand proposals</li>
  <li><strong>Care plans</strong> - translate and simplify for service users and their families</li>
  <li><strong>School communications</strong> - reach parents who speak different languages</li>
</ul>

